function TransferCard(props) { const playerData = props.playerData return (
{playerData?.name}
{playerData.position.label}
{playerData.fee.value ? playerData.fee.value : (playerData.fee.feeText === "on loan" ? "OL" : playerData.fee.feeText)}
{playerData?.fromClub}
{playerData?.toClub}
); } export default TransferCard;
